    <dd>{{% md %}}Gets or sets subscription ids list. Empty list indicates all subscriptions are selected, null indicates no update is done, explicit list indicates the explicit selected subscriptions. On insert, null is considered as bad request{{% /md %}}</dd></dl>
{{% /choosable %}}

## Import


An existing resource can be imported using its type token, name, and identifier, e.g.

```sh
$ pulumi import azure-native:marketplace:PrivateStoreCollection d0f5aa2c-ecc3-4d87-906a-f8c486dcc4f1 providers/Microsoft.Marketplace/privateStores/a0e28e55-90c4-41d8-8e34-bb7ef7775406/collections/d0f5aa2c-ecc3-4d87-906a-f8c486dcc4f1 
```
